{"tid":423251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（休班警）西九重案停職警8日內兩盜260罐奶粉落網","createTime":"2017-10-03T17:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T23:06:52.000Z","uid":29314,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"391a789f7fa74de6891ac69eefdfa7a1f9f0f606","tid":423251,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T17:37:16.000Z","msg":"一名停職男警務人員涉嫌於上月18日在屯門區一工業大廈，企圖盜去約120罐奶粉，總值約2.5萬元。其後於上月25日，他亦涉嫌於同一工業大廈盜去約140罐奶粉，總值約2.9萬元。新界北總區重案組經調查後，今日在荃灣區拘捕該名停職男警務人員，他涉嫌企圖盜竊及盜竊，現正被扣留調查。"},{"pid":"f457759702b6e99ed57ca9037c69c790ccca2bab","tid":423251,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T17:37:51.000Z","msg":"消息稱，涉案男警員隸屬西九總區重案組，已加入警隊12年，早前涉嫌欺詐警察儲蓄互助社，疑申請貸款時隱瞞自己的債務。新界北總區重案組接手跟進後，於今年4月在西九龍區，以涉嫌欺詐把他拘捕。"},{"pid":"f23ede8a1d220406ebaae499e40d0d08a11389fc","tid":423251,"uid":15086,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T17:38:04.000Z","msg":"Oh巴打唔洗跳了，恭喜"},{"pid":"60b9df9daa6baba15d131e1b6756b0705e099ed7","tid":423251,"uid":67840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T17:45:27.000Z","msg":"咁狼死"},{"pid":"c79ead47f4496ef8f397f5cb16024950e0ae9b65","tid":423251,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T18:20:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Oh巴打唔洗跳了，恭喜</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9c611012bb8ed42e40a9416e2ae262722d077c","tid":423251,"uid":50214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T18:26:21.000Z","msg":"我真係嗡唔出仲有咩機構盛產罪犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ce15fabac4e85c670991c3d3154b71aa799012","tid":423251,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T22:43:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我真係嗡唔出仲有咩機構盛產罪犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n共產黨"},{"pid":"b146d